This is a remake from the game Duke Nukem 3d From 3D realms.
The map is called "L.A. Meltdown" in the game. ive added some new things also myself.
There might be some minor bugs in the map its not fully completed. 
I didnt really learn how to add in textures to the maps thats why its missing some things here and there compared to the map of the real game.

I hope you guys like what i made so far :P.
